{"tid":1325681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反人面識別】可即應用!!! 可唔可以廣傳!!!","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:03:42.000Z","uid":259321,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eddcc4e4ddf0c8aa33178cb69d293916ea0f1910","tid":1325681,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>① 頭燈</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMqM1oB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMqM1oB.jpg&h=3a6ac677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原理: <br />\n- 利用監控相機感光元件動態範圍有限嘅弱點，喺超強反差環境下迫使相機減少曝光，令人面達至死黑。<br />\n<br />\n優點: <br />\n- 可即應用<br />\n- 因為係攻擊相機嘅物理限制所以比較有勝算<br />\n<br />\n缺點: <br />\n- 只能在黑暗環境發揮功效<br />\n- 四方八面嘅強光會令戰場環境混亂<br />\n- 萬一面部不能達到死黑仍然可以用拉curve (或最新可用AI) 重塑面部輪廓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>② 人面pattern 布料</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LE0AULO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLE0AULO.png&h=770465d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原理: <br />\n利用與人面細節相似的pattern混淆人面識別系統<br />\n<br />\n優點:<br />\n- 同樣簡單，應用不困難 <br />\n(需整T或頭巾等著物。在多人聚集時一齊著, 畫面更混亂, 所有人更安全)<br />\n<br />\n缺點: <br />\n- 效果未知 (要睇識別系統有幾聰明, 識得分辨人樣和與人樣相似嘅pattern)<br />\n<br />\n以上。"},{"pid":"a968202ce042fa7b22baeed9252c50ee5390b597","tid":1325681,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:09:36.000Z","msg":"一項更正<br />\n頭燈原理：如頭燈光環夠大，面部係會發光，等於死白。一樣識別唔到。"},{"pid":"1c88b72f41e97589868c21389c6d16c107044902","tid":1325681,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"想問下負皮果個<br />\n有乜指正<br />\n多多指教"},{"pid":"ab1d9027ae9d8378429769785c2f9c6c1165e8d2","tid":1325681,"uid":60287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"